                    </title>
                    <para>Navistar has redesigned the center side skirt panel attachment with the addition of two panel
                        brackets and has implemented a program to retrofit 9200, 9200
                        <emph type="italic">i</emph>, 9400, 9400
                        <emph type="italic">i</emph>
                        6x4 Models built between September 9, 1998 and July 1, 1999 with Code 16XPE and 16XPG chassis
                        skirts.
